INSERT INTO `Episodes` (`EpisodeID`, `Type`, `Title`, `Season`, `Story`, `Description`) VALUES
(1, 0, 'The Magician''s Apprentice', '9.1', '254a', 'The Doctor is gone. The skies of Earth have been frozen by a mysterious force. But where is the Doctor, and why is he hiding?\r\n\r\nAs his past comes back to haunt him, old enemies must meet again. Can the seemingly impossible occur? Will the Doctor and Clara escape with their lives?'),
(2, 0, 'Last Christmas', '9.X', '253', 'Clara is in for one Christmas Eve that she''s never going to forget. Reunited with the Doctor, she faces what could possibly be her last Christmas.\n\nSomething sinister lurks in an arctic base at the North Pole, and it''s beyond even the most terrible, nightmarish creatures the Doctor has faced before. Who ya gonna call? Santa Claus!'),
(4, 0, 'The Witch''s Familiar', '9.2', '254b', 'As he''s trapped in a terrifying Dalek city, the Doctor is without his sonic, without his TARDIS, and is all on his own.\n\nCan the Doctor resist his greatest temptation, and will he show his greatest enemy compassion?'),
(5, 0, 'Under the Lake', '9.3', '255a', 'Arriving on an underwater base under attack, it''s up to the Doctor and Clara to save the frightened crew. But also onboard is an alien spaceship, and the base is being haunted by the most impossible of things.\r\n\r\nThe Doctor''s deepest beliefs are challenged when he encounters something he cannot explain. Can it really be possible? Can ghosts be real?'),
(6, 0, 'Before the Flood', '9.4', '255b', 'A twisted survival plan is pieced together by an alien warlord called the Fisher King. The universe will feel the consequence. Can these events be stopped? Can the Doctor ensure the future''s coming and do the impossible?'),
(7, 0, 'The Girl Who Died', '9.5', '256a', 'Captured by Vikings, the Doctor and Clara must help protect their village from a deadly warrior race: the Mire. Outnumbered and outgunned, their fate seems inevitable. So why is the Doctor so preoccupied with a single Viking girl?'),
(8, 0, 'The Woman Who Lived', '9.6', '256b', 'A deadly highwayman called ''The Knightmare'' roams in the dark streets in England, 1651. As the Doctor searches for an unearthly element, the two come face-to-face. The Time Lord finds that things are not all as they appear. Who is the Knightmare''s sidekick? And can the Doctor protect the Earth from an enemy that has secret intentions?'),
(9, 0, 'The Zygon Invasion', '9.7', '257a', 'A long time ago, the Doctor made a deal in the Tower of London. 20 million Zygons walk among us, in human form, living undetected in peace and harmony. But cracks are showing in this delicate peace. Humans and Zygons are disappearing. In city apartment blocks, lifts are going missing, and far below the streets of Britain, alien pods are growing in secret caverns. To top it all off, UNIT''s scientific advisor, Osgood, sends a desperate message to the Doctor - but since Osgood is long dead, how is that even possible?\r\n\r\nThe Doctor, Clara and UNIT must scatter across the world in a desperate bid to set her free. But in a world of shape-shifting aliens, who can you trust? And can the world be saved before it''s too late?'),
(10, 0, 'The Zygon Inversion', '9.8', '257b', 'With the splinter group of Zygons now ahead of the Doctor, there is only one thing standing in their way of obliterating the human race and taking the Earth for themselves: a moral dilemma!\r\n\r\nIs Bonnie willing to compromise the peace already in place, just for the sake of Zygons not needing to hide, even if it means making enemies not only of humanity, but of her own race?'),
(11, 0, 'Sleep No More', '9.9', '258', 'From footage in the Le Verrier space station, the Doctor and Clara are shown to be up against terrifying Sandmen in a situation which involves sleep and lots of death.'),
(12, 0, 'Face the Raven', '9.10', '259', 'The Doctor, Clara and Rigsy are trapped on an alien street in London that is hidden from the rest of the world.\n\nAshildr, the immortal hybrid-girl, is taking care of some of the most dangerous creatures in the universe. Not everyone will get out alive; one of them must pay the price and face the raven.'),
(13, 0, 'Heaven Sent', '9.11', '260a', 'The Doctor is trapped in an old rusty castle by himself, stalked by a creature who only stops when he reveals his secrets.\n\nCan he make it through? Can he make it to safety and his home?'),
(14, 0, 'Hell Bent', '9.12', '260b', 'After being tortured for billions of years within his own confession dial, the Doctor has been pushed to the brink of madness. Returning to Gallifrey, he must face his own people, the Time Lords, but how far will he go in his quest for vengeance? Does he have another confession? And how fiercely does his rage towards them for causing Clara''s death burn?'),
(15, 0, 'The Husbands of River Song', '9.XX', '260', 'The Doctor is on the planet Mendorax Dellora in 5343, where he is asked by a man named Nardole to follow him, thinking he is a surgeon, on the orders of River Song. A surgeon is required to remove a diamond from the head of King Hydroflax after his maligned attempt to steal it, and River seeks to recover it. Surprised that River cannot identify his newest face, the Doctor struggles to break the news to her while learning how she acts on her own- and how many other lovers she has had. However, both he and River soon find that the time is drawing close for the last page in the diary of their journeys together to be written...'),
(16, 0, 'Series Nine Prologue', '9.1.1', '', 'The Doctor has returned to Karn to discuss the nature of friends and enemies with Ohila, the leader of the Sisterhood.'),
(17, 0, 'The Doctor''s Meditation', '9.1.2', '', 'As the Doctor prepares for his upcoming demise, he beds down in an unusual location.'),
(18, 0, 'Into the Dalek', '8.2', '243', 'Surrounded by his greatest enemies, the Doctor will journey into the most dangerous place in all of the universe. With the limits of his compassion being tested, the Doctor will be forced to ask a question he doesn''t know the answer to: "Am I a good man?"'),
(19, 0, 'Robot of Sherwood', '8.3', '244', 'Clara and the Doctor meet the English folk hero Robin Hood, much to the Doctor''s disbelief in the existence of someone who''s supposed to be a mere folk tale story. Traveling through Sherwood Forest in 1190, they soon realize that something is amiss, as the cruel Sheriff of Nottingham and his malevolent robot knights set in motion a plot that could rewrite the course of history for the worse.'),
(20, 0, 'Listen', '8.4', '245', 'The Doctor has been pondering a question: have people ever been truly alone? Does something lurk unseen beside us all? With Clara at his side, the Time Lord will find himself delving into familiar pasts and eerie futures. Just where does the answer to the old man''s unanswerable question lie? Will he find the answers he''s been searching for, or will his quest cost him his life this time?'),
(21, 0, 'Time Heist', '8.5', '246', 'The Doctor and Clara receive a mysterious phone call, and find themselves in a maximum security bank, memories wiped clean and two recruited strangers to accompany them. Their mission: to rob from a bank that lives up to the reputation of impregnability. But will they be able to find out what they''ve been recruited to steal and why before they get captured?'),
(22, 0, 'The Caretaker', '8.6', '247', 'The Doctor''s decision to use Clara''s school as a trap for a wild Skovox Blitzer results in revelations in her personal life. Meanwhile, the Doctor''s mechanical quarry, which has enough firepower to decimate entire planets, is running amok in the halls of Coal Hill.'),
(23, 0, 'Kill the Moon', '8.7', '248', 'The Doctor, Clara, and Courtney go visit the Moon in 2049, where they discover that the Earth''s constant companion is a little more than another mere celestial body.'),
(24, 0, 'Mummy on the Orient Express', '8.8', '249', 'After their previous trip to the moon ended on a sour note, the Doctor decides to take Clara on a final trip in the TARDIS - "our last hoorah!" The destination? There have been many trains that took the name Orient Express, but there''s only ever been one that traverses space!\r\n\r\nHowever, their their luxury trip takes an unexpected turn when they discovery there''s a supernatural passenger on board...'),
(25, 0, 'Flatline', '8.9', '250', 'Separated from the Doctor, Clara discovers a new menace from another dimension.\r\n\r\nBut how do you hide when even the walls are no protection? With people to save and the Doctor trapped, Clara comes up against an enemy that exists beyond human perception.'),
(26, 0, 'In the Forest of the Night', '8.10', '251', 'One morning, in every city and town in the world, the human race wakes up to face the most surprising invasion yet.\n\nEverywhere, in every land, a forest has grown overnight and taken back the Earth. It doesn''t take the Doctor long to discover that the final days of humanity have arrived...'),
(27, 0, 'Dark Water', '8.11', '252a', 'In the mysterious world of the Nethersphere, plans have been drawn up.\n\nMissy is about to come face to face with the Doctor, and an impossible choice is looming.\n\nThe sinister organization known only as 3W promises that "death is not an end" - but, as the Doctor and Clara discover, you might wish it was.'),
(28, 0, 'Death in Heaven', '8.12', '252b', 'With Cybermen on the streets of London, old friends unite against old enemies and the Doctor takes to the air in a startling new role.\r\n\r\nCan the mighty UNIT contain Missy? As the Doctor faces his greatest challenge, sacrifices must be made before the day is won.'),
(29, 0, 'Deep Breath', '8.1', '242', 'Shortly after his regeneration, the Doctor arrives in Victorian London, and Clara struggles to embrace the new man the Doctor has become. At the same time, they reunite with the Paternoster Gang to investigate a series of combustions that have been occurring all around the city.'),
(30, 0, 'Prequel to <i>Deep Breath</i>', '8.1.1', '', 'Strax sends a report back to Sontar concerning the Doctor''s regenerations. Meanwhile, Jenny and Vastra try to save the people of London.'),
(31, 0, 'The Night of the Doctor', '7.14.2', '', 'Still trying to skirt around the edges of the Last Great Time War, the Eighth Doctor is forced to fully join the conflict by the mysterious Sisterhood of Karn. Killed while trying to save a woman who hates him simply for being a Time Lord, the Doctor gets to choose what his next incarnation will be like. He arranges for a warrior... but makes the darkest sacrifice of his life in order to be reborn.'),
(32, 0, 'The Day of the Doctor', '7.14', '240', 'The Doctors embark on their greatest adventure in this 50th anniversary special. In the 21st century, something terrible is awakening in London''s National Gallery; in 1562, a murderous plot is afoot in Elizabethan England; and somewhere in space an ancient battle reaches its devastating conclusion. All of reality is at stake as the Doctor''s own dangerous past comes back to haunt him.'),
(33, 0, 'Strax Field Report: Trafalgar Square', '7.14.3', '', 'Field Report 1805/T: The Doctor has been sighted at the squalid human colony known as ''London''. Specifically, in ''Trafalgar Square''.'),
(34, 0, 'Strax Field Report: Queen Elizabeth', '7.14.4', '', 'Field Report Report Q235/E: Strax reports about a being the Doctor will encounter on his upcoming travels, Queen Elizabeth I.'),
(35, 0, 'Strax Field Report: The Doctors', '7.15.2', '', 'Field Report TCX11/13: Strax discusses all twelve past incarnations of the Doctor.'),
(36, 0, 'The Time of the Doctor', '7.15', '241', 'Orbiting a quiet backwater planet, the massed forces of the universe''s deadliest species gather, drawn to a mysterious message that echoes out to the stars - among them, the Doctor. Rescuing Clara from a family Christmas dinner, the Time Lord and his companion must learn what this enigmatic signal means for his own fate and that of the universe.'),
(38, 0, 'Strax Field Report: A Sontaran''s View of Christmas', '7.15.1', '', 'Field Report XI225/MAS: Strax discusses a human tradition known as ''Christmas''.'),
(39, 0, 'Strax Field Report: The Doctor Has Regenerated!', '7.15.3', '', 'Field Report Report RE12/G: Strax reports that the Doctor has once more saved the universe, but at a great cost.'),
(40, 0, 'The Last Day', '7.14.1', '', 'A Gallifreyan soldier undergoes initiation in the use of a headcam, as well as the defense of Arcadia. During his training, the impossible happens and Daleks invade.'),
(41, 0, 'Strax Field Report: The Name of the Doctor', '7.13.3', '', 'Field Report Report T713/D: Strax reports about an upcoming task he must perform; he believes the Doctor''s greatest secret is revealed...'),
(42, 0, 'Strax Field Report: A Glorious Day', '7.13.4', '', 'Field Report P137/B: A glorious day of brutality, mercilessness and property damage is almost upon us.'),
(43, 0, 'Strax Field Report: The Doctor''s Greatest Secret', '7.13.5', '', 'Field Report D895/O: The Doctor''s greatest secret has been revealed! And it has nothing to do with his chin.'),
(44, 0, 'Clarence and the Whispermen', '7.13.2', '', 'The Whisper Men approach Clarence DeMarco while in jail, producing the coordinates to Trenzalore which he must give to the ''reptile detective'' so they would end up with the Doctor.'),
(45, 0, 'She Said, He Said', '7.13.1', '', 'Shot in a dreamlike style and set in a dusty old museum, possibly located within the Doctor''s TARDIS, <i>She Said, He Said</i> sees the Doctor and Clara talking directly to the camera as they reflect on how little they really know about one another.'),
(46, 0, 'Clara and the TARDIS', '7.10.1', '', 'Clara Oswald gets into an argument with the TARDIS after the TARDIS plays a practical joke on her in the shower and then makes her bedroom disappear. After revealing to Clara that she is far from being the first girl the Doctor has "brought home," the TARDIS plays another trick on Clara that has her seeing double, and triple, and quadruple...'),
(47, 0, 'Prequel to <i>The Bells of Saint John</i>', '7.6.1', '', 'The Doctor takes a break on Earth, despondent that he can''t find Clara.'),
(48, 0, 'The Bells of Saint John', '7.6', '232', 'When Clara Oswald has problems with her Internet, she''s given a telephone number: the number of the best help line in the universe. When the Doctor answers at the other end, Clara is pulled into a life of adventure and mystery. But danger is lurking in the Wi-Fi, picking off minds and imprisoning them. "It''s like immortality, only fatal." But can the Doctor save Clara before... "I don''t know where I am!"'),
(49, 0, 'The Rings of Akhaten', '7.7', '233', 'Clara Oswald wants to see something awesome, so Eleventh Doctor whisks her off to the inhabited rings of the planet Akhaten, where the Festival of Offerings is in full swing. Clara meets the young Queen of Years as the pilgrims and natives ready for the ceremony. But something is stirring in the pyramid, and a sacrifice will be demanded.'),
(50, 0, 'Cold War', '7.8', '234', 'In 1983, the tensest point of the Cold War, a Soviet submarine discovers a strange creature frozen in the ice of the Arctic. When one of the Firebird''s crew breaks it free, it begins to attack. As the crew strikes back, the Doctor warns them that the attack could be considered a declaration of war on the entire Ice Warrior race...'),
(51, 0, 'Hide', '7.9', '235', 'Clara and the Doctor arrive at the haunted Caliburn House, set alone on a desolate moor. Within its walls, a ghost-hunting professor and a gifted empathic psychic are searching for the Witch of the Well. Her apparition appears throughout the history of the building, but is she really a ghost? And what is chasing her?'),
(52, 0, 'Journey to the Centre of the TARDIS', '7.10', '236', 'The Doctor''s TARDIS is captured by brothers running a salvage company in space. In the process, Clara gets lost inside the time machine. To save her, the Doctor promises the brothers they can have the TARDIS if they''ll help search for his missing companion. They agree, only to find that what lies at the centre of the TARDIS can kill them all.'),
(53, 0, 'The Crimson Horror', '7.11', '237', 'In 1893, the Doctor''s old friends, Vastra, Jenny Flint and Strax find an optogram of the Doctor on a victim of the mysterious ''crimson horror.'' They head for Yorkshire, where Jenny infiltrates Mrs Winifred Gillyflower''s community of Sweetville to find what has happened to him.'),
(54, 0, 'Nightmare in Silver', '7.12', '238', 'The Doctor takes Clara  and her wards, Angie and Artie, Hedgewick''s World of Wonders, a giant amusement park. The theme park is empty, occupied by a "punishment platoon" and a lone impresario with empty Cyberman shells as exhibits. The Doctor decides to stay a while, however, to investigate strange insect creatures that are roaming the park. But these insects are really machines seeking to convert the life forms on Hedgewick''s World into the newest generation of the ever-upgrading menace...'),
(55, 0, 'The Name of the Doctor', '7.13', '239', 'A prophecy is coming true. The Doctor is summoned to Trenzalore, where it is said he will fall. But what does the alleged site of his final battle have to do with the mystery of Clara - or is it Oswin? - Oswald? Can the Paternoster Gang help him avoid his apparent destiny? And most of all...Doctor who?'),
(56, 0, 'Pond Life', '7.1.1', '', 'The Doctor checks in on Amy and Rory after leaving them.'),
(57, 0, 'Prequel to <i>Asylum of the Daleks</i>', '7.1.2', '', 'The Doctor receives a message from a mysterious hooded stranger - a woman called Darla Von Karlsen wants to meet him...'),
(58, 0, 'The Making of a Gunslinger (Prequel to <i>A Town Called Mercy</i>)', '7.3.1', '', 'The cyborg that is later to be known as The Gunslinger is activated in a lab on Kahler.'),
(59, 0, 'The Inforarium', '7.4.1', '', 'The Doctor is deleting himself from history.'),
(60, 0, 'P.S.', '7.5.1', '', 'Brian Williams receives an emotional letter from his son.'),
(61, 0, 'The Great Detective', '7.X.1', '', 'Having learned of strange happenings, Madame Vastra, her maid Jenny Flint, and their Sontaran servant Strax meet with the Doctor. However, he shows no interest in the cases they mention, informing them that he has retired from investigating such matters.'),
(62, 0, 'Vastra Investigates', '7.X.2', '', 'Madame Vastra, accompanied by her loyal companions Jenny Flint and Strax, is called upon to investigate a Victorian murder mystery. But where is the Doctor?'),
(63, 0, 'Rain Gods', '7.X.3', '', 'The Doctor and River Song find themselves at the mercy of the natives of the planet of the Rain Gods, who mean to sacrifice them to their deities, until the Doctor calls upon the gods themselves to help them out of the fix.'),
(64, 0, 'Asylum of the Daleks', '7.1', '226', 'Insane Daleks are about to escape the Dalek Asylum where they are kept. The rest of the Daleks call on their greatest enemy, the Doctor, along with his companions Amy Pond and Rory Williams, to lower the defenses so they can destroy the Asylum. Can the Doctor save the day, along with his companions'' marriage, as easily as he can fix his bow-tie?'),
(65, 0, 'Dinosaurs on a Spaceship', '7.2', '227', 'In 2367, the Indian Space Agency is on high alert as an unidentified spaceship hurtles towards the Earth. The Doctor assembles a team to investigate, including the legendary Queen Nefertiti, a big game hunter named Riddell, the Ponds... and Rory''s father, Brian. Materializing aboard the mystery ship, they''re surprised to find it populated by dinosaurs. With time running out before the ship is blasted out of the sky, the Doctor must confront a vicious criminal named Solomon, as the lives of his companions and the dinosaurs hang in the balance...'),
(66, 0, 'A Town Called Mercy', '7.3', '228', 'Missing Mexico by 200 miles, the Doctor ends up in Mercy, Nevada, where something''s not quite right. The locals are hostile to strangers and a border of stone and wood surrounds the town. As the Doctor soon finds out, a gunslinger is behind this, and not just an ordinary one.'),
(67, 0, 'The Power of Three', '7.4', '229', 'There have been many ways to invade the Earth, and the Doctor has seen them all - or so he thought. And then the human race wakes up one morning and discovers the world has been overrun by small cubes, which then proceed to do nothing at all. A plan is afoot, humanity is endangered - but by what and how and, above all, when? Thus begins the Year of the Slow Invasion.\n\nFor the first time in his world-saving career the Doctor has to call upon one of the least of his virtues: patience. And the Ponds face something possibly more terrifying than any world-ending apocalypse: the Doctor is moving in!'),
(68, 0, 'The Angels Take Manhattan', '7.5', '230', 'A simple trip to New York in 2012 goes horribly wrong when Rory is sent back to the 1930s by the Weeping Angels. There, he finds that his daughter, River Song, is investigating the Angels, as Manhattan has become their hunting grounds. The Doctor and Amy must find Rory before it is too late, but what if time can''t be changed?'),
(69, 0, 'The Snowmen', '7.X', '231', 'After losing Amy and Rory, the Doctor has retired to Victorian England, where Strax, Jenny Flint, and Vastra assist him. The Doctor eventually meets Clara Oswald, and takes a liking to the young barmaid who leads a double life as a governess. At the same time, a sinister plot is unfolding; snowmen are randomly appearing around London, growing in size and power. All they need to take over the world is some human DNA in ice crystal form, and the frozen body of a drowned governess can give them just that.'),
(70, 1, 'Sky', '5.1', '', 'Sarah Jane, Clyde and Rani try to figure out why a baby abandoned on Sarah Jane''s doorstep is undergoing rapid maturation, and how she''s connected to a war between the Metalkind and the Fleshkind.'),
(71, 1, 'Sky', '5.2', '', 'Sarah Jane, Clyde and Rani try to figure out why a baby abandoned on Sarah Jane''s doorstep is undergoing rapid maturation, and how she''s connected to a war between the Metalkind and the Fleshkind.'),
(72, 1, 'The Curse of Clyde Langer', '5.3', '', 'It''s raining fish from the skies! Sarah Jane''s investigations lead the gang to the Museum of Culture, where the ancient god Hetocumtek may offer answers. Yet when Clyde touches the totem pole, his family and friends savagely turn against him and he is thrown out of their lives!'),
(73, 1, 'The Curse of Clyde Langer', '5.4', '', 'Clyde is alone and abandoned on the streets of London, living rough, cold and hungry. One person reaches out to him, but as they become friends, he''s warned about the legendary Night Dragon. In Bannerman Road, Sky knows something''s wrong â€“ why do Sarah Jane and Rani suddenly hate Clyde?'),
(74, 1, 'The Man Who Never Was', '5.5', '', 'Joseph Serf has launched his new SerfBoard, the must-have computer that no one can resist owning. Everyone wants the brand new device - and why not? What could be so dangerous about a computer?'),
(75, 1, 'The Man Who Never Was', '5.6', '', 'Joseph Serf has launched his new SerfBoard, the must-have computer that no one can resist owning. Everyone wants the brand new device - and why not? What could be so dangerous about a computer?'),
(76, 0, 'The God Complex', '6.11', '222', 'The Doctor, Amy, and Rory investigate a hotel of horror where repeat business is low, but the body count is high. A mighty monster stalks the corridors and the rooms hold visions of angels, apes, and creepy clowns. Who - or what - has brought them to this place? Can the Doctor solve the mystery before the residents check out in grisly style?'),
(77, 0, 'Night and the Doctor: Up All Night', '6.12.1', '', 'Craig discusses his fears of dealing with his son.'),
(78, 0, 'Closing Time', '6.12', '223', 'Craig Owens is having enough trouble trying to care for his child. The last thing he needed was the return of his old friend, the Doctor. And it looks like he''s not alone: trouble seems to have once again followed the Doctor to Colchester, with a silvery shine.'),
(79, 0, 'Prequel to <i>The Wedding of River Song</i>', '6.13.1', '', '<i>Tick tock, goes the clock,<br>\nTick tock, goes the clock,<br>\nTick tock, goes the clock...<br>\nDoctor, brave and good.<br>\nHe turned away from violence.<br>\nWhen he understood<br>\nThe falling of the Silence.<br></i>'),
(80, 0, 'The Wedding of River Song', '6.13', '224', 'Something is wrong. At first glance, the world seems fine, but upon closer inspection, dinosaurs, Romans, and other things throughout time have appeared. Despite the sun rising and setting like normal, the time is always the same. Oddly, nobody seems to be bothered by any of this, as if it was normal. Only the Doctor has the answer, and boy oh boy, it''s gonna be a whopper!'),
(81, 0, 'Death is the Only Answer', '6.X.1', '', 'The Doctor meets Albert Einstein and gains a fez.'),
(82, 0, 'Prequel to <i>The Doctor, the Widow, and the Wardrobe</i>', '6.X.2', '', 'The Doctor has his finger on a button that, when released, will blow up the spaceship he is currently on.'),
(83, 0, 'The Doctor, the Widow and the Wardrobe', '6.X', '225', 'Christmas Eve, 1938. Madge Arwell comes to the aid of an injured Spaceman Angel who promises to repay her kindness - all she has to do is make a wish. Three years later, Madge escapes war-torn London with her two children for a dilapidated house in Dorset. Crippled with grief at the news her husband has been lost over the English Channel, she wishes to give her children the best Christmas ever. The Arwells are greeted by the Doctor, who acts as their madcap caretaker. However, a mysterious Christmas gift from him leads them into a wintry, magical world. Madge must learn how to be braver than she ever thought possible... and that wishes can come true.'),
(84, 0, 'Good As Gold', '6.X.3', '', 'Bored of not having any adventures lately, the Doctor and Amy get a bit more than they asked for when they set out on one. Landing in London 2012, there''s only one piece of advice that can help them now: Whatever you do - don''t blink!'),
(85, 0, 'Prequel to <i>Let''s Kill Hitler</i>', '6.8.1', '', 'Amy leaves a message on the TARDIS answering machine. '),
(86, 0, 'Let''s Kill Hitler', '6.8', '219', 'Hijacked at gunpoint, the TARDIS crash-lands in 1930s Berlin. The Doctor comes face to face with the greatest war criminal in all of history - and Hitler. To save the life of one dear to him, the Doctor must teach his adversaries that time travel has responsibilities - and learns a hard lesson in the cruelest warfare of all.'),
(87, 0, 'Night Terrors', '6.9', '220', 'The Doctor receives a distress call, bringing Amy and Rory along with him to Earth. George is a young boy terrorized by the monsters in his cupboard. Are they imaginary, or are they real?'),
(88, 0, 'Night and the Doctor: First Night', '6.9.1', '', 'The night River Song is imprisoned in Stormcage for killing the Doctor, she receives a visit from her husband to take her out on their first date. Things get complicated when another River arrives.'),
(89, 0, 'Night and the Doctor: Last Night', '6.9.2', '', 'The Doctor''s first date with River has gotten more than a little complicated. With three versions of her in the TARDIS, it takes two of him to sort matters.'),
(90, 0, 'The Girl Who Waited', '6.10', '221', 'The Doctor, Amy and Rory land on Apalapucia in the middle of a plague. Amy is left behind, and the Doctor and Rory must save her...but time for Amy is running at a different speed.\r\n'),
(91, 0, 'The Gunpowder Plot', '2.1', '', 'After a run-in with a spaceship during departure, the TARDIS lands in 1605, where the crew finds the collision has caused portals to other places in time and space to open. On top of that, a group of men are plotting to assassinate the King with the help of a mysterious woman with glowing green eyes. It seems the Doctor may not be the only alien in town...'),
(92, 0, 'Miracle Day: The New World', '4.1', '', 'One day, nobody dies. All across the world, nobody dies. And then the next day, and the next and the next. People keep aging, they get hurt and sick, but they never die. The result: a population boom, overnight.\n\nWith all the extra people, resources are finite. It''s said that in four month''s time, the human race will cease to be viable. But this can''t be a natural event - someone''s got to be behind it. It''s a race against time as CIA agent Rex Matheson investigates a global conspiracy. The answers lie within an old, secret British institute. As Rex keeps asking, "What is Torchwood?", he''s drawn into a world of adventure and a threat to change what it means to be human...forever.'),
(93, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 1', '4.1.1', '', 'In 2007, Jack Harkness is kidnapped. In 2011, Miles is shot but doesn''t die. How are these two events related?'),
(94, 0, 'Miracle Day: Rendition', '4.2', '', 'Jack and Gwen travel to America by plane, while Rhys is left behind in England. Jack is poisoned en route, while Esther Drummond discovers more about Torchwood Three and those seeking to stop her. Vera Juarez attends a conference and learns there will be even more ways for the human race to run itself to painful extinction. Oswald Danes appears to a national audience, winning, of all things, sympathy.'),
(95, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 2', '4.2.1', '', 'Gwen tries to find Jack, and Holly sets up a meeting wth the mystery man.'),
(96, 0, 'Miracle Day: Dead of Night', '4.3', '', 'Torchwood goes on the run and finds a new enemy, but as they launch a raid on PhiCorp headquarters, Jack must confront the mysterious Oswald Danes.'),
(97, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 3', '4.3.1', '', 'Holly meets with the man who shot her brother, and Gwen works to find Jack.'),
(98, 0, 'Miracle Day: Escape to L.A.', '4.4', '', 'Torchwood follow PhiCorp to California to continue the fight, but walk straight into a trap. Elsewhere, Oswald Danes and Jilly Kitzinger face off against their own adversaries.'),
(99, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 4', '4.4.1', '', 'Jack dies and comes back to life, while Holly is chased by the men who shot her brother.'),
(100, 0, 'Miracle Day: The Categories of Life', '4.5', '', 'Torchwood goes undercover and discovers the terrible truth behind the Miracle. The enemy is closing in and death is about to make a shocking return.'),
(101, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 5', '4.5.1', '', 'Jack is being studied when he comes back to life, and Holly tries to get information from Miles'' computer.'),
(102, 0, 'Miracle Day: The Middle Men', '4.6', '', 'With Gwen Cooper, Rex Matheson, and Esther Drummond trapped on different sides of the Atlantic, it''s a race against time as Jack Harkness goes straight to the heart of the conspiracy.'),
(103, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 6', '4.6.1', '', 'Holly finds out who the real shooter is, and Jack continues to be experimented on.'),
(104, 0, 'Miracle Day: Immortal Sins', '4.7', '', 'Gwen must fight to protect her family. She takes a terrifying journey covering miles and decades with Jack as the long history of the Miracle is partially revealed.'),
(105, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 7', '4.7.1', '', 'Holly, Nick, and Joe arrive at Coney Island, looking for the key. Gwen attempts to save Jack.'),
(106, 0, 'Miracle Day: End of the Road', '4.8', '', 'Jack faces a showdown with a man he thought long dead, but will the outcome be beneficial? Rex Matheson takes extreme action, but is it too late to prevent the collapse of society?'),
(107, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 8', '4.8.1', '', 'Gwen struggles against Jack''s kidnapper, and Holly finds out that ending the Miracle could have serious repercussions.'),
(108, 0, 'Miracle Day: The Gathering', '4.9', '', 'As the Three Families plunge the world into recession, the Torchwood team - defeated, powerless and hunted - must strike a bargain with the devil himself.'),
(109, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 9', '4.9.1', '', 'Holly and Joe use the map to find the key, but discover something much more sinister instead. Jack manages to defeat his kidnapper.'),
(110, 0, 'Miracle Day: The Blood Line', '4.10', '', 'The Torchwood team travel around the world on a final, desperate mission; the Three Families are unstoppable unless a terrible sacrifice is made. Can the Miracle that has cursed humanity be reversed?'),
(111, 2, 'Web of Lies: Episode 10', '4.10.1', '', 'Holly makes her decision, and Jack and Gwen get the feeling they have forgotten something.'),
(112, 0, 'Prequel to <i>The Impossible Astronaut</i>', '6.1.1', '', 'Richard Nixon gets a mysterious phone call.'),
(113, 0, 'The Impossible Astronaut', '6.1', '214a', 'Amy, Rory, River and the Doctor receive a mysterious summons that takes them on an adventure to 21st century Utah and Florida in 1969.'),
(114, 0, 'Day of the Moon', '6.2', '214b', 'As Amy, Rory, and River are pursued across America by Canton Everett Delaware III and the FBI, the Doctor is locked in the perfect prison.\r\n\r\nAgainst the backdrop of the first moon landing, the Doctor and his companions must solve the mystery of the aliens and the little girl.'),
(115, 0, 'Prequel to <i>The Curse of the Black Spot</i>', '6.3.1', '', 'April 1, 1699: Captain Henry Avery writes in his journal onboard the <i>Fancy</i>.'),
(116, 0, 'The Curse of the Black Spot', '6.3', '215', 'The TARDIS is marooned onboard a 17th century pirate ship whose crew is being attacked by a mysterious and beautiful sea creature. Becalmed and beset by cabin fever, the pirates have numerous superstitious explanations for the Siren''s appearance. The Doctor has other ideas, but as his theories are disproved and every plan of escape is thwarted, he must work to win the trust of the implacable Captain Henry Avery and uncover the truth behind the pirates'' supernatural fears - and he must work quickly, for some of his friends have already fallen under the Siren''s spell.'),
(117, 0, 'Night and the Doctor: Bad Night', '6.3.2', '', 'When Amy is woken in the middle of the night by the TARDIS telephone, she learns the Doctor carries on a very active social and adventuring life while his companions sleep.'),
(118, 0, 'The Doctor''s Wife', '6.4', '216', 'The Doctor receives a message from an old Time Lord friend. The message brings him, Rory, and Amy to another universe where they meet an alien who eats TARDISes, and encounter someone very familiar...'),
(119, 0, 'Night and the Doctor: Good Night', '6.4.1', '', 'When Amy wakes to find the Doctor carrying a euphonium guiltily, she uses the opportunity to ask a question that has been bothering her for a long time.'),
(120, 0, 'The Rebel Flesh', '6.5', '217a', 'The Doctor, Amy, and Rory are visiting an acid-mining factory when solar storm hits, turning the workers'' "gangers" into self-aware individuals. The Doctor must mediate between the original workers and their rebellious gangers.'),
(121, 0, 'The Almost People', '6.6', '217b', 'As the conflict between the miners and their gangers escalates, the Doctor has to deal with Amy''s distrust of his ganger, while Rory tries to help Jennifer.'),
(122, 0, 'Prequel to <i>A Good Man Goes to War</i>', '6.7.1', '', 'Dorium Maldovar meets three shadowy figures.'),
(123, 0, 'A Good Man Goes to War', '6.7', '218', '<i>Demons run when a good man goes to war.<br>\nNight will fall and drown the sun,<br>\nWhen a good man goes to war.<br>\nFriendship dies and true love lies,<br>\nNight will fall and the dark will rise,<br>\nWhen a good man goes to war.<br>\nDemons run, but count the cost:<br>\nThe battle''s won, but the child is lost.</i>'),
(124, 0, 'The Battle of Demons Run: Two Days Later', '6.7.2', '', 'In the aftermath of the Battle of Demons Run, a battled-scarred Strax lies dead on the floor - or has he just fainted?'),
(125, 1, 'The Nightmare Man', '4.1', '', 'Luke faces life-changing events, and Bannerman Road will never be the same again. But when Sarah Jane''s son has his first nightmare, he''s haunted by a dark figure from his dreams: the Nightmare Man. A strange entity is reaching out to our world through Luke, with terrible consequences for the whole human race. With Luke, Clyde and Rani trapped in a bizarre dreamscape, Sarah Jane must fight alone. But can Luke summon the courage to face his adult life before the whole world is trapped in an endless nightmare?'),
(126, 1, 'The Nightmare Man', '4.2', '', 'Luke faces life-changing events, and Bannerman Road will never be the same again. But when Sarah Jane''s son has his first nightmare, he''s haunted by a dark figure from his dreams: the Nightmare Man. A strange entity is reaching out to our world through Luke, with terrible consequences for the whole human race. With Luke, Clyde and Rani trapped in a bizarre dreamscape, Sarah Jane must fight alone. But can Luke summon the courage to face his adult life before the whole world is trapped in an endless nightmare?'),
(127, 1, 'The Vault of Secrets', '4.3', '', 'When an old enemy, Androvax the Veil, returns to Earth asking for help, the gang face a dilemma - should they trust him? Or does the legendary Vault hold an even greater terror? A second threat arises when android guardians threaten to destroy anyone who uncovers their secrets. As the battle between Sarah Jane, Androvax and the androids reaches its climax, Rani has to save her mother from being caught in the crossfire. The Vault opens and the destiny of the entire Veil species is at stake. Is it too late to save them?'),
(128, 1, 'The Vault of Secrets', '4.4', '', 'When an old enemy, Androvax the Veil, returns to Earth asking for help, the gang face a dilemma - should they trust him? Or does the legendary Vault hold an even greater terror? A second threat arises when android guardians threaten to destroy anyone who uncovers their secrets. As the battle between Sarah Jane, Androvax and the androids reaches its climax, Rani has to save her mother from being caught in the crossfire. The Vault opens and the destiny of the entire Veil species is at stake. Is it too late to save them?'),
(129, 1, 'The Death of the Doctor', '4.5', '', 'When the Doctor is declared dead, former companions Sarah Jane and Jo Grant meet for the first time and join forces to discover the truth. As an interstellar conspiracy gathers around UNIT HQ, Clyde finds the fate of the Time Lord is in his hand - quite literally!'),
(130, 1, 'The Death of the Doctor', '4.6', '', 'When the Doctor is declared dead, former companions Sarah Jane and Jo Grant meet for the first time and join forces to discover the truth. As an interstellar conspiracy gathers around UNIT HQ, Clyde finds the fate of the Time Lord is in his hand - quite literally!'),
(131, 1, 'The Empty Planet', '4.7', '', 'Clyde and Rani are apparently the only survivors of the human race. The whole of Earth is empty - even Sarah Jane has vanished. A deserted London holds terrors of its own, mainly in the form of two mysterious and menacing robots.'),
(132, 1, 'The Empty Planet', '4.8', '', 'Clyde and Rani are apparently the only survivors of the human race. The whole of Earth is empty - even Sarah Jane has vanished. A deserted London holds terrors of its own, mainly in the form of two mysterious and menacing robots.'),
(133, 1, 'Lost in Time', '4.9', '', 'A harmless investigation turns into an epic quest across time and space as Sarah Jane and the gang are separated by the enigmatic Shopkeeper to find themselves in three different time periods, battling ghost hunters, Nazis, Tudors and a mysterious parrot called Captain!'),
(134, 1, 'Lost in Time', '4.10', '', 'A harmless investigation turns into an epic quest across time and space as Sarah Jane and the gang are separated by the enigmatic Shopkeeper to find themselves in three different time periods, battling ghost hunters, Nazis, Tudors and a mysterious parrot called Captain!'),
(135, 1, 'Goodbye, Sarah Jane Smith', '4.11', '', 'Sarah Jane realizes her ability to defend the Earth is diminishing, and that she must now hand over the task to surer hands. A seemingly suitable replacement has arrived on Bannerman Road, but can she be trusted?'),
(136, 1, 'Goodbye, Sarah Jane Smith', '4.12', '', 'Sarah Jane realizes her ability to defend the Earth is diminishing, and that she must now hand over the task to surer hands. A seemingly suitable replacement has arrived on Bannerman Road, but can she be trusted?'),
(137, 0, 'The Lodger', '5.11', '211', 'A mysterious force blocks the TARDIS - with Amy inside it - from landing, keeping it stuck in a materialization loop. It''s up to the Doctor to work out what that force is, lest Amy and the TARDIS be lost forever. As he investigates, the Doctor learns of a house on Aickman Road, with a staircase which people walk up but never come back down. To solve this mystery, the Doctor must pass himself off as a normal human and share a flat with Craig Owens.'),
(138, 0, 'The Pandorica Opens', '5.12', '212a', 'A Van Gogh painting is ferried across thousands of years, offering a terrifying prophecy, and in 102 AD, Romans receive a surprise visit from Cleopatra. Nearby, Stonehenge hides a legendary prison-box. As it slowly unlocks from the inside, terrible forces gather in the heavens. The fates are closing around the TARDIS. The Pandorica, which contains the most dangerous creature in the Universe, is opening. '),
(139, 0, 'The Big Bang', '5.13', '212b', 'The Alliance has trapped the Doctor in the Pandorica, the TARDIS has exploded with River inside, Rory has shot Amy, and the cracks have swallowed everything but the Earth and the Moon.\r\n\r\nThe fate of everything in existence lies in the hands of a little girl who still believes in stars.'),
(140, 0, 'A Christmas Carol', '5.X', '213', 'Amy and Rory are trapped on a crashing space liner, and the only way the Doctor can rescue them is to save the soul of a lonely old miser. But is Kazran Sardick beyond redemption? And what is lurking in the fogs of Christmas Eve?'),
(141, 0, 'National Television Awards 2011', '5.X.1', '', 'Dermot O''Leary wakes up late for the National Television Awards. The Doctor tries to take him there, but keeps ending up in the wrong place.'),
(142, 0, 'Space', '5.X.2', '', 'The Doctor is doing repairs on the TARDIS with Rory''s help, but thanks to Amy they make a mistake that could leave them trapped in the TARDIS forever.'),
(143, 0, 'Time', '5.X.3', '', 'The Doctor, Amy, and Rory are stuck in a space loop, trapping them in the TARDIS forever. Only one person can save them: another Amy Pond?'),
(144, 0, 'City of the Daleks', '1.1', '', 'The Doctor''s TARDIS materializes in 1963 - and London is in ruins. The Daleks have seized control of time and the only chance of saving Earth lies in a desperate quest to Kaalann, the capital city of Skaro. Hurry before time catches up with Amy, the last survivor of the human race!'),
(145, 0, 'Blood of the Cybermen', '1.2', '', 'The Doctor and Amy materialize in the Arctic, where members of a survey team are turning from flesh to metal. Something sinister is under the ice that''s been waiting thousands of years - an army of Cybermen!\r\n'),
(146, 0, 'TARDIS', '1.3', '', 'With the TARDIS caught in a time riptide, it''s up to Amy to save the day or leave the Doctor trapped in the void forever. Meanwhile, a dangerous entity is roaming the TARDIS corridors, and it hasn''t been fed for a very long time...'),
(147, 0, 'Shadows of the Vashta Nerada', '1.4', '', '23rd Century London has been devastated by a plague of biblical proportions. Now the Doctor and Amy find themselves in a deep sea base, a research station designed to study the ruins and salvage some shred of hope from the wreckage. A swarm of monstrous Vashta Nerada have invaded the facility with plans to feast on the crew. Can the Doctor and Amy survive?'),
(148, 0, 'The Eleventh Hour', '5.1', '203', 'After a literally explosive regeneration, the brand new Doctor survives a crash-landing to Earth. However, he has little time to recover: there''s a mysterious crack in a little girl''s wall and a missing alien prisoner. However, with the TARDIS damaged and the sonic screwdriver destroyed, can the Doctor capture the rogue alien before its jailers burn Earth to a crisp?'),
(149, 0, 'Meanwhile in the TARDIS 1', '5.1.1', '', 'Amy asks the Doctor many questions.'),
(150, 0, 'The Beast Below', '5.2', '204', 'For Amy''s first trip in the TARDIS, the Doctor brings his new companion to the 29th century, where all of the United Kingdom''s citizens (apart from the Scottish) live onboard Starship UK, searching for a new home amongst the stars as the Earth is being roasted by solar flares. However, the Doctor soon finds something amiss onboard the vessel. The citizens appear to fear "the smiling fellows in the booths" and ignore crying children. What secrets does Starship UK hold at its depths, and who is hiding them? Soon, the Doctor is forced to make an impossible choice. No matter what he chooses, death is the only outcome.'),
(151, 0, 'Victory of the Daleks', '5.3', '205', 'Receiving a call for help from his old friend Winston Churchill, the Doctor and Amy head for World War II to assist the Prime Minister. Once there, the Doctor reunites with his greatest enemies, the scum of the universe - the Daleks. But why are these survivors passing themselves off as man-made weapons? And why don''t they recognize the Doctor? What could these "Ironsides" have planned?'),
(152, 0, 'The Time of Angels', '5.4', '206a', 'The enigmatic River Song hurtles back into the Doctor''s life, but she''s not the only familiar face returning - the Weeping Angels are back! Following River''s calling card, the Doctor is recruited to help track down the last of the Angels, which has escaped from the Byzantium starliner and into the terrifying Maze of the Dead.'),
(153, 0, 'Flesh and Stone', '5.5', '216b', 'There''s no way back, no way up and no way out. Trapped by an army of Weeping Angels and an ever-growing mysterious crack, the Doctor and his friends try to escape through the wreckage of a crashed space liner. Meanwhile, surrounded by Angels, Amy faces an even more deadly attack, as she''s forced to find her way through the forest vault, eyes closed.'),
(154, 0, 'Weeping Angel Monster File', '5.5.1', '', 'Rastan Jovenitch wrote about Weeping Angels. But what are they?'),
(155, 0, 'Meanwhile in the TARDIS 2', '5.5.2', '', 'Amy questions the Doctor about his past companions.'),
(156, 0, 'The Vampires of Venice', '5.6', '207', 'The Doctor takes Amy and Rory, soon to be married, on a romantic trip to Venice, 1580 to make Amy focus on her relationship with her fianc&eacute;. However, things there aren''t quite what they seem.\n\nWarnings of the plague are spreading about despite having died out years before, and pale, creepy girls who don''t like sunlight are lurking around. Could it have something to do with the school run by the mysterious Rosanna Calvierri?'),
(157, 0, 'Vampires Monster File', '5.6.1', '', 'If anyone can save you from the monsters, the Doctor can. But what are ''vampires,'' anyway?'),
(158, 0, 'Amy''s Choice', '5.7', '208', 'It''s been five years since Amy last travelled with the Doctor. However, when he arrives by accident, Amy is left questioning what is real. Is she actually living with her husband Rory in Leadworth, 2015, or is she still traveling with Rory and the Doctor in the TARDIS? Which is real and which is fake? Dream or reality? Only one thing is clear: it''s Amy''s choice.'),
(159, 0, 'The Hungry Earth', '5.8', '209a', 'It''s 2020, and the most ambitious drilling project in history has reached deeper beneath the Earth''s crust than man has ever gone before - but now the ground itself is fighting back. The Doctor, Amy and Rory arrive in a tiny mining village, and find themselves plunged into a battle against a deadly danger from a bygone age.'),
(160, 0, 'Cold Blood', '5.9', '209b', 'Once more the Doctor meets members of the Silurian race. Will they be destroyed by humanity out of an act of self-preservation, or can he broker peace between them and bring about a better future for both races of planet Earth?\r\n\r\nIn the meantime, there are other questions that are left unanswered: Can Ambrose be trusted to keep Alaya alive? What is happening to Tony Mack''s wound? Are the Silurians responsible for the empty graves? And what awaits Mo and Amy when a Silurian doctor is eager to see what makes them tick?'),
(161, 0, 'Homo Reptilia Monster File', '5.9.1', '', 'Planet Earth has been invaded, but not from space and not by aliens. Humans have taken over the world of <i>Homo reptilia</i>. But what were they? And where are they?'),
(162, 0, 'Vincent and the Doctor', '5.10', '210', 'The Doctor''s trip to a museum takes turn for the worse: his interest is caught by a painting of a church by Vincent van Gogh. What troubles the Doctor is that there''s a face in the church''s window; it''s not a nice face, it''s a curious, shadowed, creepy face with a beak and nasty eyes. The Doctor knows evil when he sees it and this face is definitely evil; it may even pose a threat to the one who painted this face into the church. Only one thing will calm the Doctor''s nerves: a trip in the TARDIS to 1890 so the Doctor can find out from the artist himself.'),
(163, 0, 'The End of Time Part One', '4.17', '202a', 'It is the Tenth Doctor''s final journey - but his psychotic nemesis, the Master, has been resurrected on Christmas Eve! Each determined to cheat death, the battle rages from the abandoned wastelands of London to the mysterious Immortality Gate, whilst the alien Ood warn of an even greater danger approaching as a terrible shadow falls across the entire universe.'),
(164, 0, 'The End of Time Part Two', '4.18', '202b', 'With the sound of the drums growing louder in the Master''s head and an ancient trap closing around the Earth, the Doctor and Wilfred Mott must fight alone. Sacrifices must be made, and the deadly prophecy warns: "He will knock four times."');
INSERT INTO `Episodes` (`EpisodeID`, `Type`, `Title`, `Season`, `Story`, `Description`) VALUES
(165, 1, 'Prisoner of the Judoon', '3.1', '', 'Sarah Jane and the gang face the most dangerous day of their lives as the rhino-like Judoon return. When prisoner Androvax the Annihilator crash-lands on Earth, the Veil is set free to turn Earth''s technology against itself. His next intended victim is Sarah Jane. '),
(166, 1, 'Prisoner of the Judoon', '3.2', '', 'As the Judoon fleet approaches Earth, it''s a race against time to stop Androvax. With Genetec Systems'' technology on the rampage and Rani''s parents taken prisoner, can anything stop the Army of the Infinitesimal?'),
(167, 0, 'Androvax Alien File', '3.2.1', '', 'Rani and Mr. Smith discuss Androvax.'),
(168, 1, 'The Madwoman in the Attic', '3.3', '', 'The year is 2059. In the derelict attic of 13 Bannerman Road, an elderly Rani Chandra tells the story of the day she met the alien Eve and her life went wrong...'),
(169, 1, 'The Madwoman in the Attic', '3.4', '', 'The year is 2059. In the derelict attic of 13 Bannerman Road, an elderly Rani Chandra tells the story of the day she met the alien Eve and her life went wrong...'),
(170, 0, 'Eve Alien File', '3.4.1', '', 'Clyde asks Mr. Smith about Eve.'),
(171, 1, 'The Wedding of Sarah Jane Smith', '3.5', '', 'After Sarah Jane starts acting suspiciously, Luke, Clyde, Rani and K9 investigate. They discover she has a boyfriend, Peter Dalton, and they are going to get married. Clyde suspects Peter may be an alien. At the wedding, an old enemy returns; as the gang find themselves trapped in a time loop in Limbo, can a very special friend from the past save Sarah Jane, her friends and the entire planet Earth from the wrath of the Trickster?'),
(172, 1, 'The Wedding of Sarah Jane Smith', '3.6', '', 'After Sarah Jane starts acting suspiciously, Luke, Clyde, Rani and K9 investigate. They discover she has a boyfriend, Peter Dalton, and they are going to get married. Clyde suspects Peter may be an alien. At the wedding, an old enemy returns; as the gang find themselves trapped in a time loop in Limbo, can a very special friend from the past save Sarah Jane, her friends and the entire planet Earth from the wrath of the Trickster?'),
(173, 0, 'The Doctor Alien File', '3.6.1', '', 'Mr. Smith tells Rani about the Doctor and Gallifrey.'),
(174, 1, 'The Eternity Trap', '3.7', '', 'A haunted house, mysterious whispers and secrets in the shadows attract Sarah Jane''s attention. When Professor Rivers and the gang investigate an old legend, a monstrous creature appears in the night. The terrifying grasp of Erasmus Darkening reaches out from centuries past. Sarah Jane and the gang discover the secrets of Erasmus Darkening, but are they too late? '),
(175, 1, 'The Eternty Trap', '3.8', '', 'Ghosts from the past rise up and the quest to find the missing children reaches a climax. It seems that nothing can stop the ancient alchemist''s rise to victory.'),
(176, 0, 'Erasmus Darkening Alien File', '3.8.1', '', 'Mr Smith tells Clyde and Rani a lot about Erasmus, James Marchwood and Erasmus''s transdimensional exalurator.'),
(177, 1, 'Mona Lisa''s Revenge', '3.9', '', 'Strange forces bring the Mona Lisa, on exhibit at an art gallery in London, to life. Clyde, Rani and Luke are at the gallery on a school trip as the Mona Lisa rampages with a Sontaran blaster stolen from another painting.'),
(178, 1, 'Mona Lisa''s Revenge', '3.10', '', 'Strange forces bring the Mona Lisa, on exhibit at an art gallery in London, to life. Clyde, Rani and Luke are at the gallery on a school trip as the Mona Lisa rampages with a Sontaran blaster stolen from another painting.'),
(179, 0, 'Mona Lisa Alien File', '3.10.1', '', 'Mr. Smith tells Rani and Clyde about the Mona Lisa.'),
(180, 1, 'The Gift', '3.11', '', 'When the Slitheen''s latest scheme to destroy Earth for profit is foiled, another family from the Slitheen''s planet arrive, the Blathereen. As a generous gesture of peace, the Blathereen gift the gang with a plant called Rakweed, which could end world hunger. Meanwhile, Clyde smuggles K9 into school to help him cheat at a test, and he, Rani and the metal dog find themselves trapped in the school - surrounded by Rakweed. Can the team work together to prevent Rakweed from devouring the entire planet?'),
(181, 1, 'The Gift', '3.12', '', 'When the Slitheen''s latest scheme to destroy Earth for profit is foiled, another family from the Slitheen''s planet arrive, the Blathereen. Though they seem helpful, can they be trusted? As a generous gesture of peace, the Blathereen gift the gang with a plant called Rakweed, which could end world hunger. However, the Rakweed goes wild, spreading spores about London and infecting people, including Luke. Sarah Jane must fight alone, not only to save the Earth, but also her son. Meanwhile, Clyde smuggles K9 into school to help him cheat at a test, and he, Rani and the metal dog find themselves trapped in the school â€” surronded by Rakweed. Can the team work together across Ealing â€” and Antarctica â€” to prevent Rakweed from devouring the entire planet?'),
(182, 0, 'Blathereen Alien File', '3.12.1', '', 'Mr Smith tells Clyde about Rakweed and the Blathereen and Slitheen families.'),
(183, 0, 'Children of Earth: Day One', '3.1', '', 'When all children on Earth stop and start chanting ''We are coming,'' the Torchwood team investigates. Could this be the start of a global crisis?'),
(184, 0, 'Children of Earth: Day Two', '3.2', '', 'Torchwood Three has been blown up.. Gwen, Rhys and Ianto are on the run. Can they elude the government and save the planet from the 456?'),
(185, 0, 'Children of Earth: Day Three', '3.3', '', 'The eyes of the world turn to Britain as the 456 announce: ''We are here.'' A pillar of fire descends upon London and Torchwood must battle to protect their own families as the fight gets personal. Will Clem''s memories destroy everything?'),
(186, 0, 'Children of Earth: Day Four', '3.4', '', 'Torchwood finally learns what happened in 1965. Britain is in danger of becoming a rogue state, and everything pivots around John Frobisher as the ambassador of the 456 destroys its old allegiances.'),
(187, 0, 'Children of Earth: Day Five', '3.5', '', 'Torchwood is defenseless and Gwen Cooper stands alone. As anarchy prevails, an ordinary council estate becomes a battleground for the future of the human race.'),
(188, 0, 'Christmas Monster File', '4.14.1', '', 'Jack talks about the Sycorax, the Titanic, the Empress of the Racnoss, the Roboforms, the Roboform Christmas trees, the Graske, and the Changelings.'),
(189, 0, 'The Next Doctor', '4.14', '199', 'Christmas 1851, and Cybermen stalk Victorian London. The Doctor discovers a spate of mysterious deaths, and he''s surprised to meet another Doctor! Are two Doctors enough to stop the rise of the CyberKing?'),
(190, 0, 'Cyberman Monster File', '4.14.2', '', 'What are these metal monsters? Captain Jack explains.'),
(191, 0, 'Dreamland', '4.16.1', '', 'During a visit to a local diner, the Doctor stumbles upon a mysterious alien artifact that leads him on a mission to rescue Rivesh Mantilax from the threat of the Viperox and the clutches of the American military.'),
(192, 0, 'Tonight''s The Night (John Barrowman)', '4.14.3', '', 'Jack Harkness enters the Doctor''s TARDIS and discovers a blue-headed alien who claims to be a regenerated Doctor.'),
(193, 0, 'Planet of the Dead', '4.15', '200', 'When a London bus takes a detour to an alien world, the Doctor must join forces with the extraordinary Lady Christina. But the mysterious planet holds terrifying secrets and time is running out as the deadly Swarm gets closer...'),
(194, 0, 'The Waters of Mars', '4.16', '201', 'Mars, 2059, Bowie Base One. Last recorded message: ''Don''t drink the water. Don''t even touch it. Not one drop.'''),
(195, 0, 'Judoon Monster File', '4.8.1', '', 'Who are these mysterious, rhinoceros-like aliens?'),
(196, 0, 'Forest of the Dead', '4.9', '195b', 'Donna is gone, the Vashta Nerada are out for fresh meat and the Doctor is running out of options. Can he trust the mysterious Professor River Song, a woman who claims to be from his future? Why would his future self have given her his sonic screwdriver, or tell her his real name? And even if they do work together, can anyone stop the shadows from claiming them all as their next meal?'),
(197, 0, 'Vashta Nerada Monster File', '4.9.1', '', 'Almost every species in the universe is afraid of the dark...because there''s something in it.'),
(198, 0, 'Midnight', '4.10', '196', 'The Doctor and Donna go to the leisure planet of Midnight for a simple, relaxing holiday. However, life with the Doctor can never be that simple, and things go horribly wrong for the Doctor when he decides to go off on a bus trip to see the Sapphire Waterfall. When a mysterious entity infiltrates the shuttle bus, no one is to be trusted. Not even the Doctor himself...'),
(199, 0, 'Midnight Monster File', '4.10.1', '', 'On a planet of luxury, a dangerous monster awaits that can steal your voice and thoughts.'),
(200, 0, 'Turn Left', '4.11', '197', 'On an alien planet, Donna meets a fortune teller who launches her into a world based on one question: What would happen if Donna never met the Doctor? Without the Doctor, the whole world is in ruin, and a mysterious blonde tries to warn Donna of the oncoming darkness...Now a simple refugee, Donna is the only one who can undo the damage. But how?'),
(201, 0, 'The Trickster''s Brigade Monster File', '4.11.1', '', 'Every decision has consequences. But who decides those consequences?'),
(202, 0, 'The Stolen Earth', '4.12', '198a', 'When Earth and twenty-six other planets are stolen and the Doctor is nowhere in sight, it''s up to the combined forces of UNIT, Torchwood, Sarah Jane, and Rose to defeat the masterminds.'),
(203, 0, 'Dalek Monster File', '4.12.1', '', 'The most ruthless and terrible creatures in all the universe, the Daleks are creatures of pure evil. Or are they?'),
(204, 0, 'Journey''s End', '4.13', '198b', 'All hell has broken loose! Davros and the New Dalek Empire prepare to detonate a bomb that will wipe out all of existence. The Doctor is helpless, and the TARDIS faces destruction. The only hope lies with the Doctor''s companions - the "Children of Time" - but Dalek Caan predicts that one will die...'),
(206, 0, 'Davros Monster File', '4.13.1', '', 'He was the greatest scientist on all Skaro. But who is the man inside the chair?'),
(207, 0, 'Music of the Spheres', '4.13.2', '', 'A time and space portal has been opened between the TARDIS and...the Proms?'),
(208, 0, 'The Unicorn and the Wasp', '4.7', '194', 'In 1926, Agatha Christie mysteriously disappears, only to be found ten days later at Harrogate Hotel with no memory of what happened to her. What could have been the cause? Was it a nervous breakdown? Was it a cry for help? Or did it involve a giant alien wasp and a mysterious stranger known only as the Doctor?'),
(209, 0, 'Vespiform Monster File', '4.7.1', '', 'There are many large insect-like alien species. But only one resembles a giant wasp.'),
(210, 0, 'Silence in the Library', '4.8', '195a', 'The Doctor takes Donna to a planet-sized library in the 51st century. They find it empty of human life, and an information kiosk warns them to "count the shadows." An archaeological expedition arrives, led by the mysterious Professor River Song, who brings the cryptic last message sent from the library: "4022 saved, no survivors."'),
(211, 1, 'The Last Sontaran', '2.1', '', 'Reports of strange lights around the Tycho Project''s radio telescope lead Sarah Jane, Luke, Clyde, and Maria into a terrifying forest encounter. Sarah Jane comes face-to-face with her oldest enemy. Meanwhile, Maria wrestles with a huge decision when her dad is offered a new job in America.'),
(212, 1, 'The Last Sontaran', '2.2', '', 'Reports of strange lights around the Tycho Project''s radio telescope lead Sarah Jane, Luke, Clyde, and Maria into a terrifying forest encounter. Sarah Jane comes face-to-face with her oldest enemy. Meanwhile, Maria wrestles with a huge decision when her dad is offered a new job in America.'),
(213, 1, 'The Day of the Clown', '2.3', '', 'Rani Chandra is the new girl on Bannerman Road. She is haunted by a sinister clown. Does it have anything to do with local children who have gone missing? When Clyde''s friend Dave disappears, the trail leads to a strange circus museum and the legend of the Pied Piper.'),
(214, 1, 'The Day of the Clown', '2.4', '', 'Rani Chandra is the new girl on Bannerman Road. She is haunted by a sinister clown. Does it have anything to do with local children who have gone missing? When Clyde''s friend Dave disappears, the trail leads to a strange circus museum and the legend of the Pied Piper.'),
(215, 1, 'Secrets of the Stars', '2.5', '', 'Astrologer Martin Trueman causes a stir with his uncanny insights and predictions. Sarah Jane doesn''t believe in astrology, but she does believe that all is not as it seems with Trueman. Around her, people are falling under Trueman''s sinister spell, and even Mr. Smith doesn''t understand what''s going on.'),
(216, 1, 'Secrets of the Stars', '2.6', '', 'Astrologer Martin Trueman causes a stir with his uncanny insights and predictions. Sarah Jane doesn''t believe in astrology, but she does believe that all is not as it seems with Trueman. Around her, people are falling under Trueman''s sinister spell, and even Mr. Smith doesn''t understand what''s going on.'),
(217, 1, 'The Mark of the Berserker', '2.7', '', 'An alien pendant which gives its wearer the power to control others is stolen from Sarah Jane''s attic. Luke and Rani enlist the help of Clyde''s mum to track down Clyde and his father, who has the alien pendant.'),
(218, 1, 'The Mark of the Berserker', '2.8', '', 'An alien pendant which gives its wearer the power to control others is stolen from Sarah Jane''s attic. Luke and Rani enlist the help of Clyde''s mum to track down Clyde and his father, who has the alien pendant.'),
(219, 1, 'The Temptation of Sarah Jane Smith', '2.9', '', 'When Sarah Jane helps a boy who has slipped through a time fissure to 1951, she realizes she has found a way to meet the parents she never knew. But Luke thinks something is wrong.'),
(220, 1, 'The Temptation of Sarah Jane Smith', '2.10', '', 'When Sarah Jane helps a boy who has slipped through a time fissure to 1951, she realizes she has found a way to meet the parents she never knew. But Luke thinks something is wrong.'),
(221, 1, 'Enemy of the Bane', '2.11', '', 'Gita Chandra is kidnapped by Mrs. Wormwood, who appears to have joined forces with another of Sarah Jane''s enemies. As they prepare to settle old scores, Sarah Jane turns to an old friend.'),
(222, 1, 'Enemy of the Bane', '2.12', '', 'Gita Chandra is kidnapped by Mrs. Wormwood, who appears to have joined forces with another of Sarah Jane''s enemies. As they prepare to settle old scores, Sarah Jane turns to an old friend.'),
(223, 0, 'From Raxacoricofallipatorius with Love', '2.12.1', '', 'While she is performing maintenance on Mr. Smith, a surprising guest visits Sarah Jane.'),
(224, 0, 'Voyage of the Damned', '4.X', '188', 'A spacecraft set on an apocalyptic collision course with Earth, a host of killer robot angels and an evil severed-headed mastermind - it''s just another Christmas for the Doctor...'),
(225, 0, 'Parters in Crime', '4.1', '189', 'Donna Noble is determined to find the Doctor again - even if it means braving the villainous Miss Foster. But when the alien threat escalates out of control, can Donna find her Time Lord before the march of the Adipose begins at last?'),
(226, 0, 'Adipose Monster File', '4.1.1', '', 'Sure, they''re cute...but who are these aliens made of human flesh and bone, and how can they be stopped?'),
(227, 0, 'The Fires of Pompeii', '4.2', '190', 'The Doctor tries to take Donna to ancient Rome for her first trip in the TARDIS, but seems to have miscalculated. Instead of seven hills, they find a single mountain billowing smoke - Vesuvius. They''re in Pompeii, 23 August 79 AD: 24 hours before "Volcano Day." But something is horribly wrong. The soothsayers'' predictions seem to always be correct...so why can''t they see tomorrow''s disastrous events, the eruption of Vesuvius, the death of their city?'),
(228, 0, 'Pyrovile Monster File', '4.2.1', '', 'Vesuvius wasn''t the worst thing in Pompeii that day...'),
(229, 0, 'Planet of the Ood', '4.3', '191', 'The Doctor takes Donna to her very first alien planet: the Ood Sphere. There, the Doctor encounters the Ood once more, and red-eye strikes again. But what is causing it this time? He and Donna soon learn the horrible secrets kept by Ood Operations, and they discover just what mankind is capable of.'),
(230, 0, 'Ood Monster File', '4.3.1', '', 'Their sole purpose is to serve...or so they say.'),
(231, 0, 'The Sontaran Stratagem', '4.4', '192a', 'Fifty-two people across the world in eleven different time zones die at the exact same time. The only connection: they all have ATMOS installed in their vehicles. Martha Jones, now a UNIT medic, summons the Doctor back to modern-day Earth to help figure out why, but an old enemy lies in wait...'),
(232, 0, 'Slitheen Monster File', '4.4.1', '', 'This is one family you really don''t want to mess with.'),
(233, 0, 'The Poison Sky', '4.5', '192b', 'As ATMOS''s poisonous gas continues to thicken throughout the world, a clone of Martha works in the shadows to support the Sontarans. Will the Doctor learn about Martha''s replacement? And can he figure out how to destroy the gas before the entire planet chokes to death? More importantly, can the Doctor stop UNIT from starting an interplanetary war with the deadly Sontarans? It''s all down to Donna and Luke to fix things before it''s too late.'),
(234, 0, 'Sontaran Monster File', '4.5.1', '', 'There''s nothing more dangerous than a creature dedicated to war...'),
(235, 0, 'The Doctor''s Daughter', '4.6', '193', 'Just after finally defeating the Sontarans on modern-day Earth, the TARDIS takes the Doctor, Donna and Martha on an unexpected trip to the planet Messaline. Arriving right in the middle of a war between humans and Hath, the Doctor meets someone he thought he never would: his daughter. Can the Doctor accept a clone as his offspring, and can he stop the war before it all ends in massacre on both sides?'),
(236, 0, 'Hath Monster File', '4.6.1', '', 'As the human race spread throughout the galaxies, there one race that went with them...'),
(237, 0, 'Kiss Kiss, Bang Bang', '2.1', '', 'Jack returns with a bang, as Captain John Hart, an old friend, appears through the Rift and causes problems for the Torchwood team.'),
(238, 0, 'Sleeper', '2.2', '', 'A burglary turns into a slaughter and Torchwood suspect alien involvement. When the investigation escalates into a city-wide assault, Jack realizes the whole planet is in danger.'),
(239, 0, 'To The Last Man', '2.3', '', 'Once a year, for a single day, Tommy Brockless is defrosted in the Torchwood hub to make sure he''s still working. He is kept alive until the day he is needed and, when ghosts appear at a hospital, it''s clear that the time has come.'),
(240, 0, 'Meat', '2.4', '', 'Gwen is forced to reveal Torchwood''s true nature to Rhys after he follows her to work and accidentally uncovers the truth behind the mysterious alien meat. Is there a price to pay?'),
(241, 0, 'Adam', '2.5', '', 'An alien with the power to change memories infiltrates the team. With Jack caught up in memories of his lost family and Gwen struggling to remember Rhys, it takes Jack''s love of Ianto to reveal the truth. But there is always a price to pay.'),
(242, 0, 'Reset', '2.6', '', 'Martha Jones arrives at Torchwood after reports of numerous deaths. A medical researcher has been injecting workers with Mayflies. The Mayflies cure all illnesses before killing the patient, and Martha has got one...'),
(243, 0, 'Dead Man Walking', '2.7', '', '''I''m bringing Owen back.'' Owen has died. Jack decides to return him to life for a few minutes, but no one could have guessed the consequences.'),
(244, 0, 'A Day in the Death', '2.8', '', 'Owen chats with a suicidal woman on a rooftop, reflecting on his adjustment (or lack thereof) to his new life (or lack thereof). Will a mission with Torchwood assist in his salvation or bring about the end of the world?'),
(245, 0, 'Something Borrowed', '2.9', '', 'Gwen is about to get married to her fianc&#232; Rhys, but on her honeymoon night she is bitten by an alien and wakes up on her wedding day heavily pregnant with a shape-shifter''s baby. The alien mother is on the loose and searching for its offspring. One problem: the only way for the alien to get the egg is to rip open its carrier.'),
(246, 0, 'From Out of the Rain', '2.10', '', 'When an old cinema reopens, past horrors emerge to stalk the streets of Cardiff. As bodies are found with heartbeats but no breath, Torchwood must act fast. Who are the Night Travelers? How can Torchwood capture these mysterious breath-takers?'),
(247, 0, 'Adrift', '2.11', '', 'When a local teenager disappears, Gwen is drawn into an investigation that reveals a darker side of Torchwood. Hundreds of people have disappeared without a trace, but Jack is obstructing attempts to find them. The answer seems to lie in the rift - literally - and as Gwen follows the trail, she makes a shocking discovery.'),
(248, 0, 'Fragments', '2.12', '', 'A booby-trapped building explodes and knocks the Torchwood team unconscious. Each team member''s life flashes before his eyes. Captain Jack was initiated into a Victorian Torchwood in 1899; Tosh went on a mission to trade alien technology for her mother''s life; Ianto wooed Jack with coffee and a flair for alien-catching; and Owen lost his normal life to an alien in his fianc&#232;\r\ne''s brain.'),
(249, 0, 'Exit Wounds', '2.13', '', 'Captain John Hart returns to have his revenge on Torchwood and take Jack as his prisoner. Jack and his long lost brother Gray don''t have a good reunion.'),
(250, 0, 'Utopia', '3.11', '187a', 'As Captain Jack returns to the Doctor''s life, the TARDIS is thrown to the end of the universe. As the last remnants of humanity struggle to reach "Utopia," the Doctor''s greatest enemy is about to rise again...'),
(251, 0, 'The Sound of Drums', '3.12', '187b', 'The Doctor, Martha, and Jack return to present day London, horrified to discover that Prime Minister Harold Saxon is the Master. "Saxon" informs the world about receiving contact from an alien race called the Toclafane. Framed as fugitives, the Doctor, Martha and Jack try to sneak in and stop the Master before he unleashes a wave of terror. But his dark ambitions reach beyond the stars...'),
(252, 0, 'The Last of the Time Lords', '3.13', '187c', 'One year later, the Master and the Toclafane are rulers of Earth, which is torn apart by a year of hell. The Doctor is showing his true age, and Jack and the Jones family have been reduced to slavery on the Master''s ship. The only hope for everyone on Earth is Martha Jones, now a legend amongst humanity. As the Master prepares to turn the Earth into a giant warship that will ultimately engulf the rest of the universe, Martha must trek through dangerous territory to destroy him, but tragedy awaits her, the Doctor, and her family on the day that will pit humanity against the stars...'),
(253, 0, 'Time Crash', '3.13.1', '', 'After saying his goodbyes to Martha, the Doctor accidentally pilots his TARDIS into the path of...his past self! As the current Doctor muses over aspects of the Fifth, the Fifth Doctor becomes increasingly worried as their combined TARDISes threaten to rip a hole in space and time the size of Belgium.'),
(254, 0, 'Everything Changes', '1.1', '', 'The mysterious Torchwood team arrives at the scene of a brutal murder. PC Gwen Cooper''s curiosity is challenged by their attitude; their approach and their technology is at odds with everything she believes in. As she investigates them, she begins to uncover a dark, mysterious, and dangerous world right in the heart of Cardiff.'),
(255, 0, 'Day One', '1.2', '', 'Gwen''s first day on her new job at Torchwood sees Cardiff''s night-life at the mercy of a gaseous alien who consumes its victims during orgasm, leaving behind only dust. And it''s all her fault - she let it escape a fallen meteorite. The gas is devouring its teenage host, who fights for control as the alien inside takes down victim after victim. Torchwood tracks the alien to a sperm bank, but too late for the patrons within. If they don''t act quickly enough, it''ll be too late for everyone else too.'),
(256, 0, 'Ghost Machine', '1.3', '', 'When Gwen retrieves an alien object from a fleeing man in a hoodie, she''s haunted by a vision of a lonely young boy. As the team tracks down the object''s owner, Owen experiences an even more terrifying vision and a long-buried crime resurfaces.'),
(257, 0, 'Cyberwoman', '1.4', '', 'Ianto has a dark secret hiding in the basement of the Hub - a secret he will protect at any cost: a semi-converted Cyberwoman!'),
(258, 0, 'Small Worlds', '1.5', '', 'Jack encounters monsters from his past: fairies, with the ability to choke people and change the weather, make a series of killings centered around a little girl, the Chosen One. He also reunites with an old friend, but will Estelle Cole be safe when she starts to get a little too close to these fairies? And how can Torchwood stop a force from the dawn of time, masters of Earth, their domain? Most importantly, what is so crucial about a little girl named Jasmine, for whom these creatures will gladly tear the world apart?'),
(259, 0, 'Countrycide', '1.6', '', 'Concerned that the space-time rift is spreading, Torchwood investigates a series of gruesome deaths located in a small village in the Brecon Beacons. What sort of creature could cause such shocking injuries? Stranded without communications or equipment and isolated from one another, the team confronts a terrifying enemy.'),
(260, 0, 'Greeks Bearing Gifts', '1.7', '', 'Tosh is given an alien pendant which lets her hear other people''s thoughts. As the Torchwood team puzzle over a centuries-old skeleton, the pendant forces Tosh to question her commitment to Torchwood. Is her new-found ability a blessing or a curse?'),
(261, 0, 'They Keep Killing Suzie', '1.8', '', 'Torchwood is linked to a series of brutal murders around the city. As Jack and the team investigate, it becomes clear somebody wants their attention. What is Pilgrim, and how is it connected to a figure from Torchwood''s past? Their resurrection days are far from over: the team has no choice but to bring back Suzie.'),
(262, 0, 'Random Shoes', '1.9', '', 'A hit-and-run victim obsessed with alien life realizes that only one person can solve the mystery of his death: Gwen Cooper.'),
(263, 0, 'Out of Time', '1.10', '', 'When a plane from the 1950s lands in modern Cardiff, courtesy of the Rift, the passengers are aided by the Torchwood team as they try to adjust to a new life.'),
(264, 0, 'Combat', '1.11', '', 'Savage aliens are being kidnapped from the streets of Cardiff, and Torchwood want to know why. Owen is sent undercover to find out who''s behind it and soon befriends the charismatic Mark Lynch. Beneath the veneer of city life, Owen discovers a shocking subculture, but can he avoid being sucked in?'),
(265, 0, 'Captain Jack Harkness', '1.12', '', 'Investigating reports of ghostly music, Jack and Tosh find themselves stranded in a packed dance hall - in 1941. As Gwen, Owen and Ianto work to rescue their colleagues, Jack and Tosh meet a handsome young American squadron leader by the name of...Captain Jack Harkness.'),
(266, 0, 'End of Days', '1.13', '', 'The Rift is open and beings from all the periods of time are seeping through. What exactly does Bilis Manger know and what lurks in the rift? Can Jack save the world?'),
(267, 0, 'Invasion of the Bane', '1.X', '', 'Investigative journalist Sarah Jane Smith teams up with her new teenage neighbor Maria Jackson to face the scheming Mrs. Wormwood, the head of a company producing a popular and surprisingly addictive soft drink called "Bubble Shock!"'),
(268, 1, 'Revenge of the Slitheen', '1.1', '', 'First days at school are always difficult. For Maria and Luke, the task of blending in is made all the more difficult when their teachers turn out to be aliens from outer space, back for revenge!'),
(269, 1, 'Revenge of the Slitheen', '1.2', '', 'First days at school are always difficult. For Maria and Luke, the task of blending in is made all the more difficult when their teachers turn out to be aliens from outer space, back for revenge!'),
(270, 1, 'Eye of the Gorgon', '1.3', '', 'A haunted nursing home leads Sarah Jane to a mysterious order of nuns with an ancient - and alien - secret...'),
(271, 1, 'Eye of the Gorgon', '1.4', '', 'A haunted nursing home leads Sarah Jane to a mysterious order of nuns with an ancient - and alien - secret...'),
(272, 1, 'The Warriors of Kudlak', '1.5', '', 'Luke and Clyde try to win at Combat 3000; meanwhile, children are disappearing. And who is the mysterious Mr. Kudlak?'),
(273, 1, 'The Warriors of Kudlak', '1.6', '', 'Luke and Clyde try to win at Combat 3000; meanwhile, children are going missing. And who i the mysterious Mr. Kulak?'),
(274, 1, 'Whatever Happened to Sarah Jane?', '1.7', '', 'One day, Sarah Jane Smith exists. The next, only Maria knows of her. Andrea Yates takes her place, but Maria knows that Andrea has done something to remove Sarah Jane from the space/time continuum. It is up to Maria to uncover the identity of the "Trickster" if the human race is to survive. But with Sarah Jane and Luke wiped from existence and Clyde having lost all knowledge of his former adventures, Maria must save the world by herself. But she finds it may be time to tell her father about her secret life with Sarah Jane if the whole world is to survive.'),
(275, 1, 'Whatever Happened to Sarah Jane?', '1.8', '', 'One day, Sarah Jane Smith exists. The next, only Maria knows of her. Andrea Yates takes her place, but Maria knows that Andrea has done something to remove Sarah Jane from the space/time continuum. It is up to Maria to uncover the identity of the "Trickster" if the human race is to survive. But with Sarah Jane and Luke wiped from existence and Clyde having lost all knowledge of his former adventures, Maria must save the world by herself. But she finds it may be time to tell her father about her secret life with Sarah Jane if the whole world is to survive.'),
(276, 1, 'The Lost Boy', '1.9', '', 'A missing child turns out to be, both visually and genetically, Luke. Sarah Jane is forced to hand him over to his real parents. Heartbroken, she rejects Maria and Clyde, and with Maria''s dad threatening to sell the house to keep his daughter out of danger, it seems the gang''s adventures have come to an end. But are the Staffords really who they seem to be?'),
(277, 1, 'The Lost Boy', '1.10', '', 'A missing child turns out to be, both visually and genetically, Luke. Sarah Jane is forced to hand him over to his real parents. Heartbroken, she rejects Maria and Clyde, and with Maria''s dad threatening to sell the house to keep his daughter out of danger, it seems the gang''s adventures have come to an end. But are the Staffords really who they seem to be?'),
(278, 0, 'The Runaway Bride', '3.X', '178', 'Killer Santas, exploding baubles, an alien spaceship shaped like a giant star, and a bride mysteriously vanishing mid-wedding - Christmas with the Doctor is anything but a silent night.'),
(279, 0, 'Smith and Jones', '3.1', '179', 'Just when it seemed it would be yet another chaotic day managing her family''s disputes, Martha Jones finds trouble waiting for her at work. Trapped on the Moon with space rhinos looking for a criminal and the air running out, she will have to come to trust a seemingly mad stranger calling himself "the Doctor."'),
(280, 0, 'The Shakespeare Code', '3.2', '180', 'As a reward for her help with the Judoon, Martha gets a trip in the TARDIS. The Doctor takes her to 1599 England. After viewing a performance of Shakespeare''s latest play, the time travelers are beset by apparent sorcery. Under threat of annihilation from a species from the Dark Times, the TARDIS team have to establish whether there is a connection between a witch they''ve met and Shakespeare''s <i>Love''s Labour''s Won</i> - a play that was legendarily lost to time.'),
(281, 0, 'Gridlock', '3.3', '181', 'The Doctor takes Martha to New Earth in the far future, only to find that the entire city has become a deadly trap.'),
(282, 0, 'Daleks In Manhattan', '3.4', '182a', 'During the building of the Empire State Building in 1930''s New York City, the Cult of Skaro continues their attempts to destroy humanity and reign supreme.'),
(283, 0, 'Evolution of the Daleks', '3.5', '182b', 'As a new Dalek Empire rises in 1930''s New York City, the Doctor receives help from an unlikely ally.'),
(284, 0, 'The Lazarus Experiment', '3.6', '183', 'After traveling backwards, forwards and backwards again in time, Martha has returned home. However, before the Doctor can bid farewell to her, he hears Professor Richard Lazarus announcing that he''ll "change what it means to be human." What could this mean? And could it lead to something far more dangerous than a simple scientific failure?'),
(285, 0, '42 Prologue', '3.7.1', '', 'Erina Lessak was a trainee engineer aboard the SS Pentallian under Commander Kath McDonnell and engineer Dev Ashton.'),
(286, 0, '42', '3.7', '184', 'The Doctor and Martha follow a distress signal, only to be trapped on a spaceship hurtling towards a sun and cut off from the TARDIS. Something is on the ship and  wants everyone to burn. With only forty-two minutes left till impact, can they save the day?'),
(287, 0, 'The Infinite Quest', '3.7.2', '', 'The Doctor and Martha must find the legendary lost starship <i>the Infinite</i> before the evil Baltazar, scourge of the Galaxy, gets it.'),
(288, 0, 'Human Nature', '3.8', '185a', 'In England in 1913, school teacher John Smith experiences amazing dreams of living an incredible life as a mysterious adventurer called "the Doctor," fighting monsters, and seeing far away worlds.'),
(289, 0, 'The Family of Blood', '3.9', '185b', 'It''s 1913, and war comes to England a year early as the terrifying Family hunt for the Doctor.'),
(290, 0, 'Blink', '3.10', '186', 'In an abandoned house, the Weeping Angels wait, and the only hope to stop them is a young woman named Sally Sparrow. The only catch: the Weeping Angels can move in the blink of an eye. To defeat the ruthless enemy - with only a half of a conversation from the Doctor as help - the one rule is this: don''t turn your back, don''t look away and <i>don''t blink.</i>'),
(291, 0, 'A Ghost Story for Christmas', '3.10.1', '', '<i>Don''t blink.<br>\nBlink and you''re dead.<br>\nDon''t turn your back,<br>\nDon''t look away,<br>\nAnd <b>don''t blink.</b><br>\nGood luck.<br></i>'),
(292, 0, 'Born Again', '2.X.1', '', 'The Doctor has just regenerated into his next incarnation. But will Rose trust the Doctor now that he has a brand new face?'),
(293, 0, 'The Christmas Invasion', '2.X', '167', 'It''s Christmas Eve and high above London, the alien Sycorax are holding the Earth for ransom. The Doctor must recover from his regeneration in time to save the human race from slavery.'),
(294, 0, 'Attack of the Graske', '2.X.2', '', 'A Graske is loose and causing havoc. Can you help to stop him? Become the Doctor''s companion and save the world!'),
(295, 0, 'Tardisode 1', '2.1.1', '', 'The hospital on New Earth can cure anything. But is it hiding a more sinister secret?'),
(296, 0, 'New Earth', '2.1', '168', 'In the distant future, an order of cat-nuns cure all illnesses, but the Doctor is suspicious of their methods. He must uncover the truth and save Rose from the vengeance of his old enemy, the Lady Cassandra.'),
(297, 0, 'Tardisode 2', '2.2.1', '', 'Three hundred years ago, a meteor crashed to Earth. Now, people are mysteriously disappearing...what''s the connection?'),
(298, 0, 'Tooth and Claw', '2.2', '169', 'The Doctor and Rose have to protect Queen Victoria, but what''s chasing her?'),
(299, 0, 'Tardisode 3', '2.3.1', '', 'Mickey brings Rose and the Doctor back to Earth.'),
(300, 0, 'School Reunion', '2.3', '170', 'Deffry Vale High School is haunted at night by strange, bat-like creatures. When the Doctor investigates, he finds an old friend already on the case.'),
(301, 0, 'Tardisode 4', '2.4.1', '', 'A spaceship crashes, and the pilot receives some unwanted help.'),
(302, 0, 'The Girl in the Fireplace', '2.4', '171', 'On their first trip with Mickey, the Doctor and Rose end up on a space ship in the future that contains several portals to pre-Revolutionary France. When he steps through one of these portals, shaped like a fireplace, the Doctor discovers the even greater mystery of romantic love.'),
(303, 0, 'Tardisode 5', '2.5.1', '', 'Coming soon: the ultimate upgrade.'),
(304, 0, 'Rise of the Cybermen', '2.5', '172a', 'On a parallel Earth, a deadly new version of the Doctor''s old enemy is about to be reborn.'),
(305, 0, 'Tardisode 6', '2.6.1', '', 'The new ''skin to metal'' upgrade is not optional.'),
(306, 0, 'The Age of Steel', '2.6', '172b', 'The Cybermen take control of London and start converting the population as the Doctor, Rose, and Mickey become fugitives.'),
(307, 0, 'Tardisode 7', '2.7.1', '', 'What happens during the televised coronation of Queen Elizabeth II if something is in the TV?'),
(308, 0, 'The Idiot''s Lantern', '2.7', '173', 'It''s 1953, the coronation of Queen Elizabeth II - but there is something hiding in the televisions of the British people. Something hungry...'),
(309, 0, 'Tardisode 8', '2.8.1', '', 'And the Beast will rise from the pit.'),
(310, 0, 'The Impossible Planet', '2.8', '174a', 'The Doctor and Rose lose the TARDIS down a deep chasm, leaving themselves stranded on a space base positioned on a planet in the orbit of a black hole. Meanwhile, an entity who identifies as Satan himself is awakening and beginning to cause chaos amongst the crew.'),
(311, 0, 'Tardisode 9', '2.9.1', '', 'Something very wrong is happening because of a notebook.'),
(312, 0, 'The Satan PIt', '2.9', '174b', 'The Doctor faces off against an enemy that defies all his beliefs. Rose and what''s left of the crew are trying to escape from the Beast''s legion of possessed Ood. Can the Doctor stop an impossible enemy from escaping its prison and save the universe?'),
(313, 0, 'Tardisode 10', '2.10.1', '', 'A mysterious figure is looking for someone...'),
(314, 0, 'Love and Monsters', '2.10', '175', 'An ordinary man becomes obsessed with the Doctor and Rose Tyler and uncovers a world of living nightmares.'),
(315, 0, 'Tardisode 11', '2.11.1', '', 'Two children have gone missing, <i>CrimeCrackers</i> reports.'),
(316, 0, 'Fear Her', '2.11', '176', 'In London 2012, the Doctor and Rose set off to see the Olympics, only to find terror in the most ordinary place.'),
(317, 0, 'Tardisode 12', '2.12.1', '', '<i>I''m not mad! Torchwood exists! I know the truth about the Ghosts!</i>'),
(318, 0, 'Army of Ghosts', '2.12', '177a', 'Rose and the Doctor return to modern-day London to find a mysterious epidemic of ghosts all over the world. As the Doctor searches Torchwood Tower to find answers, something sinister lurks in the building.'),
(319, 0, 'Tardisode 13', '2.13.1', '', 'Cybermen and Daleks are everywhere as England is put under a state of emergency.'),
(320, 0, 'Doomsday', '2.13', '177b', 'A secret order of Daleks emerge and the Cybermen from Pete''s World make their way to Torchwood Tower. As the two deadly forces fight over Earth, the Doctor realizes that in order to stop the threat, sacrifices must be made.'),
(321, 0, 'Rose', '1.1', '157', 'Rose Tyler believes she is living another day of her ordinary life, but after being attacked by shop windows dummies come to life, she meets the Doctor. Her world will never be the same again.'),
(322, 0, 'The End of the World', '1.2', '158', 'The Doctor takes Rose to the year 5,000,000,000 to see the sun expand and destroy the Earth. The observation deck space station, Platform One, is holding an event with the richest beings of the time observing the Earth''s destruction, but mysterious gifts seem to be causing trouble.'),
(323, 0, 'The Unquiet Dead', '1.3', '159', 'The dead are roaming the streets of Cardiff in 1869 when the Doctor and Rose arrive, just in time for Christmas. Teaming up with Charles Dickens, the TARDIS team encounter mysterious ghosts reanimating corpses. Can they save the day?'),
(324, 0, 'Aliens of London', '1.4', '160a', 'Rose returns home to visit her family and receives a huge surprise. However, before she can explain her absence, a spaceship crashes into Big Ben, causing a worldwide crisis. Worse still, the Prime Minister has mysteriously disappeared. The Doctor''s investigation puts him in the spotlight as his long history of defending Earth finally catches up with him. Something sinister is happening at 10 Downing Street...'),
(325, 0, 'World War Three', '1.5', '160b', 'With the threat of interplanetary war looming, the human race prepare for the end, little knowing their enemies lie at the heart of the British government. As the Doctor, Rose, and new friend Harriet Jones battle for their lives in 10 Downing Street, the Slitheen family set their plans for the destruction of Earth into motion. With the world changing around him, the Doctor is powerless, and it seems only Mickey can save the world...'),
(326, 0, 'Dalek', '1.6', '161', 'The Doctor and Rose arrive in 2012 to answer a distress signal and encounter a collector of alien artifacts with one living specimen. However, the Doctor is horrified to find out that the creature is a member of a race he thought was destroyed: a Dalek.'),
(327, 0, 'The Long Game', '1.7', '162', 'Adam Mitchell takes his first trip in the TARDIS as the ship materializes on Satellite 5, a space station that broadcasts across the entire Fourth Great and Bountiful Human Empire. However, something is amiss.'),
(328, 0, 'Father''s Day', '1.8', '163', 'Pete Alan Tyler, father of Rose and husband of Jackie, died on November 7 1987. Rose was just a baby at the time; Jackie told her that nobody was there for Pete when he died and that the hit-and-run driver was never found...\r\n\r\nNow grown up, Rose asks the Ninth Doctor to take her to see him alive, but on a whim, ends up changing his fate, not realizing the consequences of such a paradox. After all, the Doctor has saved so many lives...what could the real consequences be over a man alive in the world who wasn''t alive before?'),
(329, 0, 'The Empty Child', '1.9', '164a', 'Chasing a metallic object through the Time Vortex, the Doctor and Rose  arrive in London during the Blitz. While Rose encounters Captain Jack Harkness, the dashing Time Agent responsible for bringing the object, the Doctor meets a group of homeless children terrorized by Jamie, an "empty" child wearing a gas mask.'),
(330, 0, 'The Doctor Dances', '1.10', '164b', 'The Child''s plague is spreading throughout wartime London, and its zombie army is on the march. The Doctor and Rose form an alliance with intergalactic con man Captain Jack, but find themselves trapped in the abandoned hospital. They head to the crash site of Jack''s supposed space junk and discover the ground zero for the mysterious plague.'),
(331, 0, 'Boom Town', '1.11', '165', 'The Doctor, Rose, and Jack travel to modern-day Cardiff and meet up with Rose''s boyfriend, Mickey. There, they discover that their enemy, Blon Fel-Fotch Passameer-Day Slitheen, is very much alive, if without an easy escape route from Earth, and is...creating a nuclear power plant?'),
(332, 0, 'Bad Wolf', '1.12', '166a', 'Separated and with no TARDIS, the Doctor, Rose, and Jack have to fight for their lives on board the Game Station, but a far more dangerous threat is lurking, just out of sight. The entire human race has been blinded to the threat on its doorstep, and Armageddon is fast approaching.'),
(333, 0, 'The Parting of the Ways', '1.13', '166b', 'As the Daleks attack the Game Station led by their Emperor, the Doctor finds himself helpless. He knows he must make big sacrifices if he is going to survive. But does this mean losing his beloved Rose forever?\r\n\r\nWith Jack assembling an army together and the Doctor powerless against the Dalek Emperor, a deadly net closes around the whole universe. One thing is for certain: not everyone will make it out of this deadly battle alive. But who or what is Bad Wolf? It''s time for the Doctor and Rose to find out.'),
(334, 0, 'The Trickster and Krislok the Graske', '4.2.1', '', 'Sarah Jane recounts her dealings with the Trickster and Krislok the Graske.'),
(335, 0, 'The Pied Piper, Ship, and Eve', '4.4.1', '', 'Rani and Mr. Smith update the Alien Files with data about the Pied Piper, Ship, and Eve.'),
(336, 0, 'Sontarans, Wormwood, and the Bane Mother', '4.6.1', '', 'On his mum''s instructions, Luke updates the Alien Files with what he knows about Mrs. Wormwood, the Bane Mother, and the Sontarans.'),
(337, 0, 'Slitheen, Blathereen, and Rakweed', '4.8.1', '', 'Sarah Jane adds the Slitheen and Blathereen families, as well as the Blathereen''s gift of Rakweed, to the Alien Files.'),
(338, 0, 'The Berserkers and the Mona Lisa', '4.10.1', '', 'Clyde updates the Alien Files with information on the Berserkers and the Mona Lisa.'),
(339, 0, 'The Judoon, Mister Dread, and Androvax', '4.12.1', '', 'Luke comes back home from Oxford for a visit, but finds a note from his mum informing him that she, Clyde, and Rani are away on an investigation. While home alone, he helps Mr. Smith update the Alien Files with data on the Judoon and his encounter with the Androvax. Mr. Smith then relates the story of Androvax''s return to Earth, and the involvement of Mister Dread and the Men in Black, to Luke and further updates the Alien Files.');
